node.text: Why?? 😳🐶 He looks so cute but he’s really mean.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Mark Wahlberg on July 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, beard and outdoors.

node.text: Bullying and cruelty for any reason is wrong. We made this movie for the Joe Bells of the world. My hope is that you leave the theaters with more understanding and support for those around you: your child, your coworker, your community member. At the end of the day — no matter our differences — we are ALL human and deserving of love and compassion. ❤️🙏❤️ @joebellthemovie is in theaters now. #ThankYouJoeBell  www.joebellthemovie.com
